<div class="campaigns-container">
  <div class="campaigns-header">
    <h2>Xhunt Earn 活动配置</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="campaigns-toolbar">
    <div class="left">
      <span class="muted">dataId: <code id="campaigns-dataid">xhunt_campaigns</code></span>
      <span class="muted">group: <code>DEFAULT_GROUP</code></span>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <div class="campaigns-search">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"></path></svg>
        <input
          id="campaigns-search"
          type="text"
          placeholder="搜索活动..."
        />
      </div>
      <button class="btn primary" id="campaigns-refresh">刷新</button>
      <button class="btn" id="campaigns-new">新增</button>
      <button class="btn" id="campaigns-duplicate" disabled>复制</button>
      <button class="btn danger" id="campaigns-delete" disabled>删除</button>
      <button class="btn success" id="campaigns-publish" disabled>发布</button>
      <button class="btn" id="campaigns-sync-website">同步到网站</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaigns-body">
    <div class="list">
      <div class="list-header">
        <button type="button" class="list-toggle" id="campaigns-list-toggle" title="收起列表" aria-label="收起列表">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="list-header-text">
          <span>活动列表</span>
          <span class="muted" id="campaigns-count">0</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="list-items" id="campaigns-list"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="editor">
      <div class="editor-header">
        <div>
          <span>编辑活动</span>
          <span class="muted" id="campaigns-editor-hint">选择左侧活动开始编辑</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="campaigns-editor-empty" class="editor-empty">
        <div class="empty-title">请选择一个活动</div>
        <div class="empty-desc">
          从左侧列表选择活动进行编辑，或点击「新增」创建活动
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="campaigns-editor-body" style="display: none">
        <!-- 第一层：活动状态控制（最核心） -->
        <div class="campaign-status-control">
          <div class="status-control-primary">
            <label class="switch-label switch-label-primary">展示活动</label>
            <label class="switch switch-primary">
              <input id="campaigns-enabled" type="checkbox" disabled />
              <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="status-control-secondary">
            <label class="switch-label">测试模式（仅内部可见）</label>
            <label class="switch">
              <input id="campaigns-testingPhase" type="checkbox" disabled />
              <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 第二层：基础配置（关键信息） -->
        <div class="field-row field-row-basic">
          <div class="field field-primary">
            <label>活动ID</label>
            <input id="campaigns-twitter-handle" type="text" placeholder="例如：mantle" />
            <div class="field-hint">例如：mantle3,bybit2，可找技术确认</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field field-secondary">
            <label>排序权重</label>
            <input id="campaigns-sortWeight" type="number" min="0" max="10000" step="1" placeholder="0" />
            <div class="field-hint">0-10000，数值越大越靠前</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 第三层：选项开关（可选功能） -->
        <div class="campaign-options">
          <div class="option-item">
            <label class="switch-label">
              <span>早期项目风险提示</span>
              <span class="risk-preview-trigger" title="查看预览">ℹ️</span>
            </label>
            <label class="switch">
              <input id="campaigns-hasRiskConfirm" type="checkbox" disabled />
              <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
            <div class="field-hint">在活动页面显示早期项目风险提示</div>
            <div class="risk-preview-popup" id="risk-preview-popup" style="display: none;">
              <div class="risk-preview-content">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px;">中文预览：</div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">
                  <strong>重要提示：</strong>该项目为 Early-stage 项目，信息由项目方提供，请在参与前自行判断。点击继续即表示理解并接受。
                </div>
                <div style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px;">English Preview:</div>
                <div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">
                  <strong>Important Notice:</strong> The project is in its early stage. The information is provided by the project team. Please make an informed decision before participating. Proceeding indicates that you understand and accept this.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="option-item">
            <label class="switch-label">显示付费推广政策</label>
            <label class="switch">
              <input id="campaigns-showSponsoredPolicy" type="checkbox" disabled />
              <span class="slider"></span>
            </label>
            <div class="field-hint">在报名按钮上方显示「付费推广政策」提示</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field-row field-row-1" id="campaigns-legacy-info" style="display:none; margin-bottom: 12px;">
          <div class="field">
            <div class="muted" style="padding: 10px 12px; border:1px dashed #f59e0b; border-radius:10px; background:#fffbeb; color:#92400e; line-height:1.6;">ℹ️ 当前正在编辑“网页独有数据 / 插件已下架数据”。这类活动已不在 Nacos 中，所以只支持网站数据库配置，不展示 Nacos 配置部分。</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-compact">
          <div class="section-title">活动信息</div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>标题（中文）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-displayName-zh" type="text" />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>标题（English）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-displayName-en" type="text" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>短标题（中文）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-copy-shortTitle-zh" type="text" />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>短标题（English）</label>
              <input id="campaigns-copy-shortTitle-en" type="text" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-block">
            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>项目介绍（中文）</label>
                <textarea
                  id="campaigns-projectIntroduction-zh"
                  rows="2"
                  placeholder="纯文本介绍..."
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>项目介绍（English）</label>
                <textarea
                  id="campaigns-projectIntroduction-en"
                  rows="2"
                  placeholder="Plain text introduction..."
                ></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-block">
            <div class="section-title-inline">
              <span>写作主题</span>
              <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-writing-themes-add" type="button" disabled>
                +添加
              </button>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="repeaters-hint">← 左右滑动 · 至少保留一个主题</div> -->
            <div class="repeaters-horizontal" id="campaigns-writing-themes"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-compact">
          <div class="section-title">时间、奖励与门槛</div>
          
          <!-- 第一层：活动时间 -->
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-sm">⏰ 活动时间</div>
            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>开始时间</label>
                <input id="campaigns-startAt" type="datetime-local" />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>结束时间</label>
                <input id="campaigns-endAt" type="datetime-local" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- 第二层：POI 基础奖励 -->
          <div class="section-sub reward-tier reward-tier-primary">
            <div class="reward-tier-header">
              <span class="reward-tier-title">🎯 POI 基础奖励</span>
              <span class="reward-tier-badge">核心</span>
            </div>
            <div class="field-row field-row-3">
              <div class="field">
                <label>奖励金额</label>
                <input id="campaigns-rewardAmount" type="number" min="1" max="99999999" placeholder="1-99999999" />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>人数</label>
                <input id="campaigns-rewardParticipantCount" type="number" min="10" max="1000" placeholder="10-1000" />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>分配机制</label>
                <select id="campaigns-rewardDistributionType">
                  <option value="">请选择</option>
                  <option value="equal">平分</option>
                  <option value="mindshare">mindshare</option>
                  <option value="workshare">workshare</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>奖励单位</label>
                <input id="campaigns-rewardUnit" type="text" placeholder="USDT" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- 第三层：POW 榜单（开关控制） -->
          <div class="section-sub reward-tier reward-tier-optional">
            <div class="reward-tier-header">
              <div class="reward-tier-title-wrapper">
                <span class="reward-tier-title">⛏️ POW 榜单</span>
                <span class="reward-tier-desc">按工作量证明排名发奖</span>
              </div>
              <div class="field field-inline" style="margin: 0;">
                <label class="switch-label">开启</label>
                <label class="switch">
                  <input id="campaigns-enablePowLeaderboard" type="checkbox" disabled />
                  <span class="slider"></span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="pow-leaderboard-fields" style="display: none;">
              <div class="reward-tier-content">
                <div class="field-row field-row-3">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label>POW奖励金额</label>
                    <input id="campaigns-powAmount" type="number" min="0" placeholder="0" />
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label>POW获奖人数</label>
                    <input id="campaigns-powWinnerCount" type="number" min="1" placeholder="10" />
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label>POW分配机制</label>
                    <select id="campaigns-powDistributionType">
                      <option value="">请选择</option>
                      <option value="equal">平分</option>
                      <option value="mindshare">mindshare</option>
                      <option value="workshare">workshare</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="field-row field-row-2">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label>POW奖励单位</label>
                    <input id="campaigns-powUnit" type="text" placeholder="USDT" />
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- 第四层：征文大赛（开关控制） -->
          <div class="section-sub reward-tier reward-tier-optional">
            <div class="reward-tier-header">
              <div class="reward-tier-title-wrapper">
                <span class="reward-tier-title">✍️ 征文大赛</span>
                <span class="reward-tier-desc">高质量内容创作奖励</span>
              </div>
              <div class="field field-inline" style="margin: 0;">
                <label class="switch-label">开启</label>
                <label class="switch">
                  <input id="campaigns-enableEssayContest" type="checkbox" disabled />
                  <span class="slider"></span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="essay-contest-fields" style="display: none;">
              <div class="reward-tier-content">
                <div class="field-row field-row-3">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label>征文大赛金额</label>
                    <input id="campaigns-essayContestAmount" type="number" min="0" placeholder="0" />
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label>获奖人数</label>
                    <input id="campaigns-essayContestWinnerCount" type="number" min="1" placeholder="10" />
                  </div>
                  <div class="field">
                    <label>奖励单位（选填）</label>
                    <input id="campaigns-essayContestUnit" type="text" placeholder="USDT" />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section section-collapsible" style="margin-top: 6px;">
                  <div class="section-title section-title-collapsible">
                    <span>征文大赛获奖名单</span>
                    <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-essay-winners-add" type="button" disabled>+添加</button>
                    <span class="section-toggle">▼</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="section-content" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="repeaters" id="campaigns-essay-winners"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- 第五层：报名门槛 -->
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-sm">🚪 报名门槛</div>
            <div class="field-row">
              <div class="field">
                <select id="campaigns-threshold">
                  <option value="">请选择</option>
                  <option value="50k">50k</option>
                  <option value="100k">100k</option>
                  <option value="200k">200k</option>
                  <option value="200k+creator">200k+creator</option>
                </select>
                <div class="muted" style="margin-top: 3px; font-size: 11px;">硬性条件：注册早于1个月且分数≥50</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-compact">
          <div class="section-title">链接 · 名单 · 报名文案</div>
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-sm">相关链接</div>
            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>A.推特活动指南链接</label>
                <input id="campaigns-links-guideUrl" type="text" placeholder="https://..." />
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>B.官网活动页面链接</label>
                <input id="campaigns-links-activeUrl" type="text" placeholder="https://..." />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="field-row">
              <div class="field">
                <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">插件榜单底部显示「查看官方排行榜」（跳转到 B.官网活动页面链接）</label>
                <label class="switch">
                  <input id="campaigns-links-showLeaderboardLink" type="checkbox" disabled />
                  <span class="slider"></span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-sm">相关名单（每行一个）</div>
            <div class="field-row field-row-2">
              <div class="field">
                <label>内部测试人员（测试阶段可见的人）</label>
                <textarea id="campaigns-testList" rows="2" placeholder="luoyukun4"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="field">
                <label>‼️在插件里面哪些推特号右侧展示本活动</label>
                <textarea id="campaigns-targetUserIds" rows="2" placeholder="bybit_web3&#10;Bybit__Alpha"></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section section-collapsible" style="margin-top: 6px;">
            <div class="section-title section-title-collapsible">
              <span>报名按钮文案（通常不改）</span>
              <span class="section-toggle">▼</span>
            </div>
            <div class="section-content" style="display: none;">
              <div class="field-row field-row-3">
                <div class="field">
                  <label>emoji</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-copy-emoji" type="text" placeholder="🎉" />
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                  <label>ctaText（zh）</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-copy-ctaText-zh" type="text" />
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                  <label>ctaText（en）</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-copy-ctaText-en" type="text" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="field-row field-row-2">
                <div class="field">
                  <label>去官方（zh/en）</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-copy-goToOfficialText-zh" type="text" placeholder="zh" style="margin-bottom:4px" />
                  <input id="campaigns-copy-goToOfficialText-en" type="text" placeholder="en" />
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                  <label>查看指南（zh/en）</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-copy-viewGuideText-zh" type="text" placeholder="zh" style="margin-bottom:4px" />
                  <input id="campaigns-copy-viewGuideText-en" type="text" placeholder="en" />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-compact">
          <div class="section-title">Logo · 任务 · Tags</div>
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-sm">
              活动方 logo
              <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-logos-add" type="button" disabled>+添加</button>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="repeaters-hint">← 左右滑动</div> -->
            <div class="repeaters" id="campaigns-logos"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-sm">
              报名前需完成的任务
              <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-tasks-add" type="button" disabled>+添加</button>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="repeaters-hint">← 左右滑动</div> -->
            <div class="repeaters" id="campaigns-tasks"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-sm">
              活动 Tags（可选）
              <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-tags-add" type="button" disabled>+添加</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tag-notice">
              <span class="tag-notice-icon">ℹ️</span>
              <span class="tag-notice-text">如果配置了自定义 Tag，前端本身会自动生成的【按贡献】【征文大赛】【TOP200】都将被替换</span>
            </div>
            <div class="repeaters" id="campaigns-tags"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section section-compact campaigns-website-section">
          <div class="section-title">网站专属配置</div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-3">
            <div class="field">
              <label>网站状态</label>
              <select id="campaigns-webStatus">
                <option value="draft">draft（草稿）</option>
                <option value="coming_soon">coming_soon（即将上线）</option>
                <option value="live">live（展示中）</option>
                <option value="claim">claim（领奖中）</option>
                <option value="ended">ended（已结束）</option>
                <option value="archived">archived（归档）</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>详情页 slug</label>
              <input id="campaigns-website-slug" type="text" placeholder="默认等于 campaignKey" />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>页面模板</label>
              <input id="campaigns-pageTemplate" type="text" placeholder="standard" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>网站公告（中文）</label>
              <textarea id="campaigns-webAnnouncementZh" rows="2"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>Website Announcement (English)</label>
              <textarea id="campaigns-webAnnouncementEn" rows="2"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>奖励文案（中文）</label>
              <textarea id="campaigns-webRewardTextZh" rows="2"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>Reward Text (English)</label>
              <textarea id="campaigns-webRewardTextEn" rows="2"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label>备注（中文）</label>
              <textarea id="campaigns-webNoteZh" rows="2"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>Note (English)</label>
              <textarea id="campaigns-webNoteEn" rows="2"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="campaigns-claim-config">
            <div class="section-sub">
              <div class="section-title-sm">领奖配置（claim 状态必填校验）</div>
              <div class="muted" id="campaigns-claim-hint" style="margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.6;">claim 状态下需要填写领奖相关字段</div>
              <div class="field-row field-row-1">
                <div class="field">
                  <label>POI 合约地址（必填）</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-claimPoiContractAddress" type="text" placeholder="0x..." />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="field-row field-row-2">
                <div class="field" id="campaigns-claim-pow-field">
                  <label>POW 合约地址（按 Nacos 开关校验）</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-claimPowContractAddress" type="text" placeholder="0x..." />
                </div>
                <div class="field" id="campaigns-claim-essay-field">
                  <label>征文大赛合约地址（按 Nacos 开关校验）</label>
                  <input id="campaigns-claimEssayContractAddress" type="text" placeholder="0x..." />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="section-sub">
            <div class="section-title-inline">
              <span>模板配置（JSON）</span>
              <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;">
                <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-templateConfig-format" type="button" disabled>格式化 JSON</button>
                <button class="btn btn-sm" id="campaigns-templateConfig-copy" type="button" disabled>复制 JSON</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="field-row field-row-1">
              <div class="field">
                <textarea id="campaigns-templateConfig" rows="10" placeholder='{"claimStatusBadge":"Claim is live"}'></textarea>
                <div class="field-hint">建议填写合法 JSON。保存前会自动校验；可先点“格式化 JSON”检查结构。</div>
                <div class="muted" id="campaigns-templateConfig-status" style="margin-top:6px; line-height:1.5;">JSON 状态：未检查</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field-row field-row-1">
            <div class="field">
